cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the use of saliency maps in deep reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CV, followed by cs.HC and cs.NE.
